        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/lingsha/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1036150-2.jpg" alt="FUMI" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/30699470/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/30699470/" class="">第177页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/lingsha/" class=" " title="FUMI">FUMI</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="30699470">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">访谈者在使用访谈提纲时一定要保持一种开放、灵活的态度。访谈的具体形式应该因人、因具体情景而异，不必拘泥于同一程式，也不必强行按照访谈提纲的语言和顺序提问。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2014-02-28 01:04</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>访谈者在使用访谈提纲时一定要保持一种开放、灵活的态度。访谈的具体形式应该因人、因具体情景而异，不必拘泥于同一程式，也不必强行按照访谈提纲的语言和顺序提问。</q></blockquote>
